reviewText: This is a very old movie and the rating is not on the seller, it is on the movie as compared to todays standard.  They are okay movies, nice to have and add to my collection of Marine movies.  The seller got it to me a great time.  The action is these movies is very mild compare to todays movie making.  But, I enjoyed watching it, it is a good change from todays computer aided movies.
Got it for the old Marine in the family. He said it was pretty good.
